I think many people today

00:00:14.910 --> 00:00:16.379 align:middle line:84%
don't know what to
believe anymore.

00:00:16.379 --> 00:00:20.104 align:middle line:84%
>> People are basically going
to keep on to help uncover what

00:00:20.104 --> 00:00:20.770 align:middle line:90%
really happened.

00:00:20.770 --> 00:00:23.170 align:middle line:84%
>> I felt like something
was watching me.

00:00:23.170 --> 00:00:25.220 align:middle line:84%
>> We weren't given
