And she ordered a
$500 bottle of wine.

00:07:52.255 --> 00:07:53.130 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: Oh, no.

00:07:53.130 --> 00:07:53.810 align:middle line:90%
First date?

00:07:53.810 --> 00:07:54.980 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: First date.

