00:08:10.160 --> 00:08:11.460 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: It was in LA.

00:08:11.460 --> 00:08:13.870 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: And I'm a
matchmaker in Southern

00:08:13.870 --> 00:08:14.840 align:middle line:90%
California.

00:08:14.840 --> 00:08:18.080 align:middle line:84%
And there tends to be some high
maintenance ladies out there,

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:18.580 align:middle line:90%
you know?

00:08:18.580 --> 00:08:20.669 align:middle line:84%
And the more
beautiful the woman,

00:08:20.669 --> 00:08:22.460 align:middle line:84%
they get a lot of
opportunities and they're

00:08:22.460 --> 00:08:24.510 align:middle line:90%
dating the wealthy guys.

00:08:24.510 --> 00:08:27.522 align:middle line:84%
And they think that
they're entitled to that.

00:08:27.522 --> 00:08:30.540 align:middle line:84%
And that's pretty sad,
because the truth is,

00:08:30.540 --> 00:08:33.220 align:middle line:84%
