00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:37.440 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: How important
is money, finances,

00:08:37.440 --> 00:08:38.750 align:middle line:90%
in a relationship?

00:08:38.750 --> 00:08:42.500 align:middle line:84%
Because we, as guys, we hear
all kinds of things about women,

00:08:42.500 --> 00:08:46.720 align:middle line:84%
that some of them may be
gold diggers, others are not.

00:08:46.720 --> 00:08:48.490 align:middle line:90%
But how important is that?

00:08:48.490 --> 00:08:51.080 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: Well it's, and
especially I see it in the big

00:08:51.080 --> 00:08:53.010 align:middle line:90%
cities, you know.

00:08:53.010 --> 00:08:55.542 align:middle line:84%
So in LA the women will
see the Red Carpet events.

00:08:55.542 --> 00:08:58.000 align:middle line:84%
They'll see the guys with the
private jets and the Bentleys

00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:58.640 align:middle line:90%
and everything.

00:08:58.640 --> 00:08:59.848 align:middle line:90%
They think, well I want that.

00:08:59.848 --> 00:09:01.430 align:middle line:90%
I deserve that.

00:09:01.430 --> 00:09:03.090 align:middle line:84%
So that can even be
a block for women,

00:09:03.090 --> 00:09:05.215 align:middle line:84%
when they're waiting for
a guy with a lot of money.

00:09:05.215 --> 00:09:09.290 align:middle line:84%
And now we have a recession
and everyone has got to work.

00:09:09.290 --> 00:09:11.590 align:middle line:90%
So it's a big deal.

00:09:11.590 --> 00:09:13.320 align:middle line:84%
And in a relationship
it's a big deal.

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:16.310 align:middle line:84%
You've got to talk about those
things before you get married,

00:09:16.310 --> 00:09:19.177 align:middle line:84%
because you want to find out,
is your significant other,

00:09:19.177 --> 00:09:19.760 align:middle line:90%
is he in debt?

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:20.740 align:middle line:84%
What do they think
about marriage?

00:09:20.740 --> 00:09:22.656 align:middle line:84%
What do you think about
saving for retirement?

00:09:22.656 --> 00:09:24.119 align:middle line:84%
These are big
things that come up,

00:09:24.119 --> 00:09:26.410 align:middle line:84%
problems in a marriage, if
you didn't discuss it first.

00:09:26.410 --> 00:09:28.970 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Money
doesn't make you happy.

00:09:28.970 --> 00:09:31.430 align:middle line:84%
It makes it easy, but it
doesn't make you happy.

00:09:31.430 --> 00:09:32.360 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: It
doesn't make you happy.

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:34.560 align:middle line:84%
You hear about people with a lot
of money and they're miserable.

00:09:34.560 --> 00:09:35.360 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: They're miserable.

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:35.620 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: Yeah.

00:09:35.620 --> 00:09:38.330 align:middle line:84%
So it's really, you have to
be happy with yourself first,

00:09:38.330 --> 00:09:39.950 align:middle line:84%
before you get in
a relationship.

00:09:39.950 --> 00:09:42.480 align:middle line:84%
When you're happy
with your life,

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:45.070 align:middle line:84%
you know, then you're happy with
however much money you have.

00:09:45.070 --> 00:09:45.760 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Interesting.

00:09:45.760 --> 00:09:46.260 align:middle line:90%
All right.

00:09:46.260 --> 00:09:48.040 align:middle line:84%
Let's do a little
screening test.

00:09:48.040 --> 00:09:49.810 align:middle line:84%
Let's assume I come
to you as a client.

00:09:49.810 --> 00:09:50.710 align:middle line:90%
What do we do?

00:09:50.710 --> 00:09:51.710 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: All right.

00:09:51.710 --> 00:09:53.770 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: What's this
going to cost me?

00:09:53.770 --> 00:09:57.730 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: George, what's
your limit on your credit card?

00:09:57.730 --> 00:09:58.509 align:middle line:90%
Just kidding.

00:09:58.509 --> 00:09:59.550 align:middle line:90%
So what are you looking--

00:09:59.550 --> 00:10:00.828 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Mine is maxed.

00:10:00.828 --> 00:10:02.110 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:10:02.110 --> 00:10:03.110 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: All right.

00:10:03.110 --> 00:10:05.584 align:middle line:84%
So I would want to know
what your history has been.

00:10:05.584 --> 00:10:06.292 align:middle line:90%
Are you divorced?

00:10:06.292 --> 00:10:07.670 align:middle line:90%
Have you been married before?

00:10:07.670 --> 00:10:10.500 align:middle line:84%
If you're gotten to your age
now without ever being married,

00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:11.579 align:middle line:90%
why?

00:10:11.579 --> 00:10:12.620 align:middle line:90%
What are you looking for?

00:10:12.620 --> 00:10:14.078 align:middle line:84%
What age range are
you looking for?

00:10:14.078 --> 00:10:15.080 align:middle line:90%
Do you have kids?

00:10:15.080 --> 00:10:16.107 align:middle line:90%
Do you want kids?

00:10:16.107 --> 00:10:17.690 align:middle line:84%
So I need to know
all of these things,

00:10:17.690 --> 00:10:20.080 align:middle line:84%
because let's say,
you never had any kids

00:10:20.080 --> 00:10:21.874 align:middle line:84%
and you would like
to have a family.

00:10:21.874 --> 00:10:24.040 align:middle line:84%
So I'm going to have to
look for women in, probably,

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:24.962 align:middle line:90%
in her '30s for you.

00:10:24.962 --> 00:10:26.420 align:middle line:84%
You know '40s is
not going to work.

00:10:26.420 --> 00:10:28.740 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: So you have
to go that in depth?

00:10:28.740 --> 00:10:31.070 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: I do, because
they want a life partner.

00:10:31.070 --> 00:10:31.805 align:middle line:84%
And those are the
considerations.

00:10:31.805 --> 00:10:33.597 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: And if guy
doesn't want a family?

00:10:33.597 --> 00:10:36.096 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: Right, so maybe
he'll date a woman who already

00:10:36.096 --> 00:10:38.180 align:middle line:84%
has children, or someone
who could go either way,

00:10:38.180 --> 00:10:38.929 align:middle line:90%
it doesn't matter.

00:10:38.929 --> 00:10:39.620 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Huh!

00:10:39.620 --> 00:10:40.120 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:10:40.120 --> 00:10:41.280 align:middle line:90%
So you screen him.

00:10:41.280 --> 00:10:42.610 align:middle line:90%
You ask him questions.

00:10:42.610 --> 00:10:43.915 align:middle line:90%
Do you put it in a computer?

00:10:43.915 --> 00:10:45.290 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: No,
you know, well,

00:10:45.290 --> 00:10:47.090 align:middle line:84%
I have some things
on the computer.

00:10:47.090 --> 00:10:48.660 align:middle line:90%
But I make a nice bio on him.

00:10:48.660 --> 00:10:49.856 align:middle line:90%
And I type that up.

00:10:49.856 --> 00:10:52.230 align:middle line:84%
