>> MARTENSON: Well, usually,
the men are my paying clients,

00:10:59.370 --> 00:11:00.140 align:middle line:90%
for the most part.

00:11:00.140 --> 00:11:01.360 align:middle line:90%
And I do send it to him first.

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.960 align:middle line:84%
I said, you know, I
have this great lady.

00:11:02.960 --> 00:11:04.160 align:middle line:84%
And I give him a
bio and picture.

00:11:04.160 --> 00:11:05.160 align:middle line:90%
Would you be interested?

00:11:05.160 --> 00:11:07.850 align:middle line:84%
If he says yes, then
I'll send her his info.

00:11:07.850 --> 00:11:09.980 align:middle line:84%
If she says, yes, then
I give him her number.

00:11:09.980 --> 00:11:12.460 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Have you ever sent
a bio out without the picture

00:11:12.460 --> 00:11:13.136 align:middle line:90%
