will they take my word for it.

00:11:24.209 --> 00:11:26.000 align:middle line:84%
And I'm like, that's
what you hired me for.

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:26.510 align:middle line:90%
You know.

00:11:26.510 --> 00:11:28.301 align:middle line:84%
If you want to pick
people out of pictures,

00:11:28.301 --> 00:11:29.680 align:middle line:90%
go on the internet.

00:11:29.680 --> 00:11:31.350 align:middle line:84%
But they still want
to see the photos.

00:11:31.350 --> 00:11:33.860 align:middle line:84%
So if that makes them
comfortable, then I do that.

00:11:33.860 --> 00:11:36.950 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Well, I've got friends
who would go on the dating

00:11:36.950 --> 00:11:41.610 align:middle line:84%
