And they're upset, or
something didn't work out.

00:11:48.680 --> 00:11:49.980 align:middle line:90%
Why would somebody do that?

00:11:49.980 --> 00:11:51.605 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: That
happened to me once.

00:11:51.605 --> 00:11:54.267 align:middle line:84%
Oh, before I met my
