00:11:54.267 --> 00:11:56.850 align:middle line:84%
because my cousin and my aunts
insisted, you've got to try it,

00:11:56.850 --> 00:11:57.725 align:middle line:90%
you've got to try it.

00:11:57.725 --> 00:11:59.620 align:middle line:84%
It was after I moved
back from Chicago.

00:11:59.620 --> 00:12:02.590 align:middle line:84%
I saw this guy,
he looked so cute,

00:12:02.590 --> 00:12:05.046 align:middle line:84%
