00:12:05.046 --> 00:12:07.170 align:middle line:84%
And I could just picture
myself kissing those lips.

00:12:07.170 --> 00:12:08.030 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: You look
for a guy's lips?

00:12:08.030 --> 00:12:09.280 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: Well, I just
liked his lips, all right?

00:12:09.280 --> 00:12:10.680 align:middle line:84%
