Something about his
voice and personality

00:12:15.380 --> 00:12:16.850 align:middle line:90%
didn't match that picture.

00:12:16.850 --> 00:12:20.634 align:middle line:84%
And then when I met
him, he had thin lips.

00:12:20.634 --> 00:12:22.300 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Well maybe
his Botox wore off.

00:12:22.300 --> 00:12:23.570 align:middle line:90%
Or whether they put in there.

00:12:23.570 --> 00:12:24.680 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: Yeah, deflated.

00:12:24.680 --> 00:12:25.770 align:middle line:90%
And then I said, you know what?

00:12:25.770 --> 00:12:27.180 align:middle line:84%
I said, you really don't
look like your picture.

00:12:27.180 --> 00:12:28.755 align:middle line:84%
And then he's, oh, well,
that was an old picture,

00:12:28.755 --> 00:12:30.910 align:middle line:84%
and my hair was lighter,
and brushing it off.

00:12:30.910 --> 00:12:32.880 align:middle line:84%
And about an hour into
it I said, I'm sorry,

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:34.930 align:middle line:84%
but you really don't
look like your picture.

00:12:34.930 --> 00:12:38.360 align:middle line:84%
And he said, oh,
I'll admit, that I

00:12:38.360 --> 00:12:39.922 align:middle line:90%
put a model's picture up there.

00:12:39.922 --> 00:12:40.880 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Unbelievable.

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:41.880 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: And I said, why?

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:42.570 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: It wasn't
him him, at all?

00:12:42.570 --> 00:12:43.278 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: No.

00:12:43.278 --> 00:12:44.810 align:middle line:84%
And he says,
because I'm a doctor

00:12:44.810 --> 00:12:47.385 align:middle line:84%
and I didn't want anybody at
the hospital to see my picture.

00:12:47.385 --> 00:12:48.040 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Well, then
don't put a picture up.

00:12:48.040 --> 00:12:49.780 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: And I said, well,
if you're that embarrassed you

00:12:49.780 --> 00:12:50.390 align:middle line:90%
shouldn't be up there.

00:12:50.390 --> 00:12:50.730 align:middle line:90%
>> NOORY: Exactly.

00:12:50.730 --> 00:12:52.021 align:middle line:90%
>> MARTENSON: And he says, hey.

00:12:52.021 --> 00:12:54.700 align:middle line:84%
He says, Marla, some woman
actually got me get mad at me

00:12:54.700 --> 00:12:55.500 align:middle line:90%
when they find out.

00:12:55.500 --> 00:12:57.320 align:middle line:84%
