nice about it.

00:12:57.320 --> 00:12:59.320 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: Let's take some
questions for you, OK?

00:12:59.320 --> 00:13:02.210 align:middle line:84%
Marla Martenson, the
Beverly Hills Matchmaker,

00:13:02.210 --> 00:13:04.030 align:middle line:90%
who's got a question for her?

00:13:04.030 --> 00:13:06.820 align:middle line:84%
I know somebody
wants to date, right?

00:13:06.820 --> 00:13:07.750 align:middle line:90%
Yes, sir.

00:13:07.750 --> 00:13:10.540 align:middle line:84%
>> AUDIENCE: Marla, what's
the process you used to pick

00:13:10.540 --> 00:13:11.530 align:middle line:90%
your husband?

00:13:11.530 --> 00:13:15.050 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: Oh, the
process that I used?

00:13:15.050 --> 00:13:17.250 align:middle line:84%
This was great, because
I met my husband

00:13:17.250 --> 00:13:20.114 align:middle line:84%
after I had-- so I had
been married prior.

00:13:20.114 --> 00:13:21.530 align:middle line:84%
And then I had
five years of being

00:13:21.530 --> 00:13:23.370 align:middle line:90%
single when I was in Chicago.

00:13:23.370 --> 00:13:24.920 align:middle line:90%
And then I came back to LA.

00:13:24.920 --> 00:13:27.290 align:middle line:84%
And when I was single, I
was dating all the bad boys,

00:13:27.290 --> 00:13:29.610 align:middle line:84%
I was always getting
my heart broken.

00:13:29.610 --> 00:13:32.440 align:middle line:84%
And I was used to
guys going out with me

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:35.240 align:middle line:84%
and then never calling
again, which a lot of women

00:13:35.240 --> 00:13:37.210 align:middle line:90%
have experienced.

00:13:37.210 --> 00:13:40.120 align:middle line:84%
And so when I met him,
through a mutual friend,

00:13:40.120 --> 00:13:42.880 align:middle line:84%
we hit it off right away and
he seemed to really like me.

00:13:42.880 --> 00:13:46.454 align:middle line:84%
But in my mind I was like, maybe
he'll-- I figured he probably

00:13:46.454 --> 00:13:47.370 align:middle line:90%
won't ever call again.

00:13:47.370 --> 00:13:49.244 align:middle line:84%
So I said, if he calls
again, he calls again.

00:13:49.244 --> 00:13:50.340 align:middle line:90%
If he doesn't, he doesn't.

00:13:50.340 --> 00:13:52.427 align:middle line:84%
And I was really working
on myself at the time.

00:13:52.427 --> 00:13:54.010 align:middle line:84%
My father had passed
away, I was doing

00:13:54.010 --> 00:13:56.330 align:middle line:84%
a lot of healing and
working on my career

00:13:56.330 --> 00:13:58.320 align:middle line:84%
and my spiritual
side, and everything.

00:13:58.320 --> 00:14:01.690 align:middle line:84%
And it was interesting, because
he just kept calling every day.

00:14:01.690 --> 00:14:04.672 align:middle line:84%
And within three weeks
it was my birthday,

00:14:04.672 --> 00:14:06.130 align:middle line:84%
and he had a birthday
party for me.

00:14:06.130 --> 00:14:08.610 align:middle line:84%
And he was introducing me to
his friends as his girlfriend.

00:14:08.610 --> 00:14:09.880 align:middle line:90%
This is my girlfriend, Marla.

00:14:09.880 --> 00:14:13.317 align:middle line:84%
And using the words we
in our future-- well, we.

00:14:13.317 --> 00:14:14.900 align:middle line:84%
>> NOORY: You pick
up on those things.

00:14:14.900 --> 00:14:16.240 align:middle line:84%
>> MARTENSON: Yeah, you pick
up on those things which other

00:14:16.240 --> 00:14:17.550 align:middle line:90%
guys never did.

00:14:17.550 --> 00:14:19.410 align:middle line:84%
So I knew that he
was really serious.

00:14:19.410 --> 00:14:21.720 align:middle line:90%
And he was just a great guy.

00:14:21.720 --> 00:14:24.080 align:middle line:84%
And he was dating a couple
of girls when he met me.

